    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2ccbae4a115cf3e1a9e63c4cb95fe738.poster.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2ccbae4a115cf3e1a9e63c4cb95fe738.webm?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>这是一场冒险，唯一的目标是击败恶魔。每次你踏上旅程，都必须在众多选项中做出选择。是探索陌生的洞穴，与恶魔战斗，还是寻找这个世界的秘密？不要忘记你必须对自己的行动负责…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/b063eff6a8b252fab6b6aed9b73a33a0.poster.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/b063eff6a8b252fab6b6aed9b73a33a0.webm?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/b063eff6a8b252fab6b6aed9b73a33a0.mp4?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/597a8d30174a4fd56d284dedab73f7eb.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>每一步都要做出决定，引领你走向目标的命运之路。</i><br></li><li><i>不要害怕与恶魔搏斗到死。</i><br></li><li><i>选择你的玩法风格、职业和技能。</i><br></li><li><i>购买或制作装备、神器和药剂来生存下去。</i><br></li><li><i>寻找新的定居点和愿意帮助你的人。</i><br></li><li><i>改变这个世界的命运，或被邪恶吞噬。</i></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.poster.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.webm?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.mp4?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/1347e3100d8c7f705e34efe03b468da0.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=72 /></span><br><br>《<strong>Weak Soul</strong>》讲述了一个被恶魔入侵的中世纪大陆的故事。故事发生在一个末日后的黑暗奇幻世界中。在探索世界的过程中，会有各种事件出现。可以选择不帮助任何人，参与抢劫并变得自私，或者通过善行来增加你的善业因果，期待成就中的好运。<br><br>在达到目标的过程中，你将不得不杀死无数的恶魔，经常死亡并遭受痛苦。但只有很少的人能够忍受并走到最后…<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/b2d624e483f188d4d95e5a488e254169.webp?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=48 /></span>",
